Following similar logic, I created similar solution for [Spring Boot context][1].

Dependency in addition to spring boot 3.1.3+ depedencies:

    &lt;dependency&gt;
			&lt;groupId&gt;org.reflections&lt;/groupId&gt;
			&lt;artifactId&gt;reflections&lt;/artifactId&gt;
